src/components/ForceGraphComponent.react.description:
ForceGraphComponent displays a force-directed graph
from provided graphData.

id.description: The ID used to identify this compnent in Dash callbacks

requestContent.description: Will return information on selected node

graphData.description:
Takes a {'node': {}, 'links': {}} object encoded as a string
(not sure why we need to encode this as a string, but
 propTypes.Object didn't seem to work)

setProps.description:
Dash-assigned callback that should be called whenever any of the
properties change
